      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n<b>WHITE ALBUM2</b><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly91cGxvYWQud2lraW1lZGlhLm9yZy93aWtpcGVkaWEvZW4vNy83OC9XaGl0ZV9BbGJ1bV8yLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/7/78/White_Album_2.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/7/78/White_Album_2.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/7/78/White_Album_2.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n懂的人都懂，誉为拖宅神作，你玩了她你就不想碰别的galgame<br/>\n因为过于完美，其他的作品都感到逊色。<br/>\n<br/>\n<b>月に寄りそう乙女の作法</b><br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly91cGxvYWQud2lraW1lZGlhLm9yZy93aWtpcGVkaWEvemgvOC84OS9Uc3VyaW90by5qcGc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/89/Tsurioto.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/89/Tsurioto.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/89/Tsurioto.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n女装系列的巅峰，至今无人超越，剧情一流<br/>\n毕竟是王雀孙执笔的<br/>\n<br/>\n<b>抜きゲーみたいな島に住んでる貧乳はどうすりゃいいですか?1＆２</b><br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9wYnMudHdpbWcuY29tL2NhcmRfaW1nLzE3Nzg1NzQ0NTcxNTE2NDM2NDgvbXhmZHpUdzk_Zm9ybWF0PWpwZyZuYW1lPTkwMHg5MDA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/card_img/1778574457151643648/mxfdzTw9?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\"><img alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/card_img/1778574457151643648/mxfdzTw9?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/card_img/1778574457151643648/mxfdzTw9?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<b>现代galgame大成之作，标题欺诈的纯剧情作，日式梗非常的密集</b><br/>\n<b>骨折王子永远的神</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<b>金色ラブリッチェ</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9wYnMudHdpbWcuY29tL21lZGlhL0V4VEk3dmZVNEFFb0tkUz9mb3JtYXQ9anBnJm5hbWU9bGFyZ2U\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ExTI7vfU4AEoKdS?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\"><img alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ExTI7vfU4AEoKdS?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ExTI7vfU4AEoKdS?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<b>当年的大满贯，伞哥nb，</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<b>この青空に約束を―</b><br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly91cGxvYWQud2lraW1lZGlhLm9yZy93aWtpcGVkaWEvZW4vNi82Yi9Lb25vX0Fvem9yYV9uaV9ZYWt1c29rdV9vX1BDX2dhbWUuanBn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/6/6b/Kono_Aozora_ni_Yakusoku_o_PC_game.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/6/6b/Kono_Aozora_ni_Yakusoku_o_PC_game.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/6/6b/Kono_Aozora_ni_Yakusoku_o_PC_game.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<b>丸户老贼胃疼的三角恋的开端，请多来点，求你了</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>グリザイアの果実系列</b><br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly91cGxvYWQud2lraW1lZGlhLm9yZy93aWtpcGVkaWEvZW4vZC9kMi9HcmlzYWlhX25vX0thaml0c3UucG5n\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/d2/Grisaia_no_Kajitsu.png\"><img alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/d2/Grisaia_no_Kajitsu.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/d2/Grisaia_no_Kajitsu.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<b>剧情，声优，音乐皆为上乘之作。</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>BALDR SKY Dive1＆2</b><br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly91cGxvYWQud2lraW1lZGlhLm9yZy93aWtpcGVkaWEvZW4vNC80Yy9CQUxEUl9TS1lfRGl2ZTElRTIlODAlOUNMb3N0TWVtb3J5JUUyJTgwJTlEX2dhbWVfY292ZXIuanBn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/4/4c/BALDR_SKY_Dive1%E2%80%9CLostMemory%E2%80%9D_game_cover.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/4/4c/BALDR_SKY_Dive1%E2%80%9CLostMemory%E2%80%9D_game_cover.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/4/4c/BALDR_SKY_Dive1%E2%80%9CLostMemory%E2%80%9D_game_cover.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<b>戏画巅峰之作，游戏性极强，剧情也可圈可点。</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>ヘンタイ・プリズン</b><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvY2RlMzY5MjZlY2FlNWJlNzFkMjNiLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDI0JmhlaWdodD02MjA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cde36926ecae5be71d23b.jpg?width=1024&amp;height=620\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cde36926ecae5be71d23b.jpg?width=1024&amp;height=620\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/cde36926ecae5be71d23b.jpg?width=1024&amp;height=620\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<b>骨折王子又一大作，非常有哲学性的作品，探讨了性与自由，我本人非常推荐的作品。</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>パルフェ 〜ショコラ second brew</b><br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9wYnMudHdpbWcuY29tL21lZGlhL0V3Mk45SHZWRUFZR1JqcD9mb3JtYXQ9cG5nJm5hbWU9c21hbGw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ew2N9HvVEAYGRjp?format=png&amp;name=orig\"><img alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ew2N9HvVEAYGRjp?format=png&amp;name=orig\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ew2N9HvVEAYGRjp?format=png&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<b>已经被重置2次的丸户大作，戏画倒了现在可能入手困难吧。</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>さくらの雲＊スカアレットの恋</b><br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9wYnMudHdpbWcuY29tL21lZGlhL0VlNE5lT01VOEFFaWMyMz9mb3JtYXQ9anBnJm5hbWU9bGFyZ2U\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ee4NeOMU8AEic23?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\"><img alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ee4NeOMU8AEic23?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Ee4NeOMU8AEic23?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<b>时代不是令和还是我樱云嗒。</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>世界でいちばんNG（だめ）な恋</b><br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9wYnMudHdpbWcuY29tL21lZGlhL0ZVZTMta0VVc0FBN0Faaz9mb3JtYXQ9anBnJm5hbWU9OTAweDkwMA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FUe3-kEUsAA7AZk?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\"><img alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FUe3-kEUsAA7AZk?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/FUe3-kEUsAA7AZk?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<b>丸户绝杀。我最喜欢的作品，</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>神採りアルケミーマイスター</b><br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9wYnMudHdpbWcuY29tL21lZGlhL0Y2cmwxbk9hVUFBUTl6Tz9mb3JtYXQ9anBnJm5hbWU9bGFyZ2U\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/F6rl1nOaUAAQ9zO?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\"><img alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/F6rl1nOaUAAQ9zO?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/F6rl1nOaUAAQ9zO?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<b>壮哉我大E社，大E社SLG游戏模式的最高杰作。</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>ChuSingura46＋1　-忠臣蔵46＋1-</b><br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9wYnMudHdpbWcuY29tL21lZGlhL0ItdlI4RkdVRUFBVzdFOT9mb3JtYXQ9anBnJm5hbWU9OTAweDkwMA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/B-vR8FGUEAAW7E9?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\"><img alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/B-vR8FGUEAAW7E9?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/B-vR8FGUEAAW7E9?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<b>穿越轮回题材galgame的巅峰，</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>ノラと皇女と野良猫ハート -Nora, Princess, and Stray Cat.-</b><br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9wYnMudHdpbWcuY29tL21lZGlhL0VxQXVLaXVWb0FFcjJOYT9mb3JtYXQ9anBnJm5hbWU9bGFyZ2U\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EqAuKiuVoAEr2Na?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\"><img alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EqAuKiuVoAEr2Na?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EqAuKiuVoAEr2Na?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<b>童话一样温柔而暖心的爱情故事，hato的能力上限作品</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>景の海のアペイリア</b><br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9wYnMudHdpbWcuY29tL21lZGlhL0RBMW9MTHlVSUFBUklvWj9mb3JtYXQ9anBnJm5hbWU9bGFyZ2U\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DA1oLLyUIAARIoZ?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\"><img alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DA1oLLyUIAARIoZ?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DA1oLLyUIAARIoZ?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<b>科幻题材烧脑神作，</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>俺たちに翼はない</b><br/>\n<b><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9wYnMudHdpbWcuY29tL21lZGlhL0V5T0l3dm5WY0FBekttdz9mb3JtYXQ9anBnJm5hbWU9bGFyZ2U\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EyOIwvnVcAAzKmw?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\"><img alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EyOIwvnVcAAzKmw?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EyOIwvnVcAAzKmw?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a></b><br/>\n<b>多重人格主角的非常特别的优秀作品。</b><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>先放这么多，这些如果你认真玩1年都玩不完。</b> </div>",
